                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Mogetius <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Pudens <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>dom</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> Dinace <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXXV <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIII <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>gem</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XI <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius <lb n="9"/>Primus <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende Fragmente einer Grabstele, horizontal bei Z. 4 gebrochen. Zeile 1: ET-Ligatur; VS außerhalb des Inschriftfeldes; Zeile 2: S außerhalb des Inschriftfeldes; Zeile 3: INA-Ligatur, E außerhalb des Inschriftfeldes; Zeile 6: I klein am Zeilenende. Datierung: Aufenthalt der legio XIII gemina in Vindobona/Wien.</p>
            </div>
